{
  "stem": "7722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who was killed was killed, who wasn't, the other fell on the top of him, and he-- and he suffocated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was only-- I was only told one thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Ukrainian told me that they-- a few days [INAUDIBLE], the [INAUDIBLE] was moving, because probably they were still over there, people not killed-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] not killed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, I'm sitting here before you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went through, and I still cannot believe the human being can be so barbaric.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, too, [SOBBING] a wild animal will not eat their own kind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And here, human beings-- it's worse than eating-- are killing their own kind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Human beings are worse than animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to leave him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to leave and I went to Karpo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, the first-- the man who worked for me was Homa-- his name was Homa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He worked for us for 20 years, he worked for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I wouldn't praise myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people who worked for me, if I could bring them here, they would tell you [CRYING] how I treat them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I want to tell you, and I want to tell you one, just give you an example.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were girls working for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was in-- when I was in hiding, by this guy-- so they used to make their own, they called it [NON-ENGLISH], their own vodka.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he got drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got-- he got drunk, and he-- and he told-- and when he told them, do you know who-- who is in my barn?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I was-- with this guy, I wasn't in the barn already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was in the beginning, you see, he had-- what?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
